title: Recently remodeled 2 bedroom plus office in NE Minneapolis
posting_body: ["Beautiful recently remodeled 2 bedroom plus office in a quiet 1880's Victorian converted to a 4-plex.", ' Lower unit in a 4-plex with high ceilings and a ton of Victorian charm in NE Minneapolis.', '•\tRecently remodel', '•\tHardwood floors throughout, tall tin ceilings, tall windows', '•\t2 bedrooms and an office/den, one of the bedrooms is huge', '•\tNo pets', '•\tNot section 8 approved', '•\tLots of closet space, walk-in hallway closet, walk-in bedroom closet', '•\tOn site coin-op laundry in basement (3 washers and 3 dryers), direct access to basement from apartment.', '•\tAdditional storage in basement (~70sqft)', '•\tApartment has dedicated water heater, no need to race the neighbors for a hot shower :)', '•\tWalk to restaurants, shops, and brew houses (Hazels, Sarah Janes, The Bag Lady, The Coffee Shop NE, Fare Game, Sociable Cider Werks, Fair State Brewing, Bauhaus Brew Labs, Holy Land, El Taco Riendo, Khao Hom Thai, The Mill, MOMO Sushi, and so much more)', '•\t2 parks within 3 blocks', '•\tOn street parking only, but it’s never an issue finding parking right in front of building.', '•\t1 block to busline', '•\tNo smoking in building', 'Available Sept 1st or Oct 1st.', ' Can be earlier, let us know what you’re looking for.', '$1550/month plus electric and gas utilities', '$1550 sec.', 'deposit', '1 year lease and then month to month', 'following the 1 year lease.', 'This property is not section 8 approved and does not allow pets.', 'Please mention Lincoln St when replying to this add.']
